name: The Lost HicEtNuncs
description: The first 152 HitEtNunc NFTs were minted on a different contract, while the site was still being developed, and are thus not accessible via the current UI, and may never be. However they persist on the blockchain. This SVG NFT makes them accessible directly from IPFS. "Right Click"-->"Open In New Tab" on the thumbnails to load the full media (where possible), the square to see the metadata and the circle to go to the creator wallet (where i was able to find it).
